short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bypasses the memorable info page on Lloyds online banking.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This tool is used to autofill your Lloyds Banking Memorable Information, you can set your memorable information within the extension, then when you login to lloyds the information will be autofilled!

This extension is open source with the source code viewable here:
https://github.com/tonyaellie/lloyds-bypass
